# Hyperboloid Demo Scene
# Beautiful hyperboloid showcase

# Camera - angled view to see the shape better
C 4,4,-8   -0.3,-0.3,1   70

# Ambient lighting
A 0.2   255,255,255

# Main light source
L 8,10,-5   0.7   255,255,255

# Central red hyperboloid - classic hourglass shape
hy 0,0,0   1.5   -2.5,2.5   255,50,50

# Blue hyperboloid - narrower
hy 4,0,3   0.8   -2,2   50,100,255

# Green hyperboloid - wider and taller
hy -4,0,3   2.0   -3,3   50,255,100

# Floor plane for reference
pl 0,-3,0   0,1,0   150,150,150

# Background sphere
sp 0,0,15   3   100,100,200
